### Assignments API - Archimedes Python Service
### Teacher: create/list assignments. Student: list by course, start activity, post completion.
### Base URL: http://localhost:8001

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001
@apiVersion = /api/v1

###############################################################################
### VARIABLES (replace with values from auth/courses responses)
###############################################################################
@courseId = 510bfa8b-c900-4225-a7da-59bcb9015450
@teacherId = d0e03591-18c8-494f-901e-5bfd145d24bf
@studentId = 789e0123-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002
@assignmentId = 5e4d26cc-9c9a-478f-82fc-e9fd1117aa02
@accessToken = your_access_token_here

###############################################################################
### STUDENT FLOW: List assignments → Start (content_url / activity_id) → Post completion
###############################################################################
# 1) Student page: list assignments for a course (getAssignmentsByCourse)
# 2) "Start": open activity via assignment.activity.content_url or use activity_id with worksheet/session
# 3) After worksheet/miniquiz done: postAssignmentCompletion(assignmentId, { student_id, score }, accessToken)

### Student – Get assignments for a course (getAssignmentsByCourse)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Student – Record completion after finishing worksheet/miniquiz (postAssignmentCompletion)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/completions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "score": 85
}

###############################################################################
### TEACHER: Create and list assignments
###############################################################################

### Teacher – Create assignment
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "course_id": "{{courseId}}",
  "activity_id": "EX01",
  "teacher_id": "{{teacherId}}",
  "due_date": "2026-03-21T00:00:00Z",
  "title_override": null
}

### List assignments for a course (teacher or student)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments/courses/{{courseId}}

### Teacher – "All my assignments" (getAssignmentsByTeacher)
# Use for a single view of every assignment the teacher has created across all courses.
# Helper: getAssignmentsByTeacher(teacherId) → GET /assignments/teachers/{teacher_id}
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments/teachers/{{teacherId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Teacher – List assignments for one of their courses (ownership checked)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/teachers/{{teacherId}}/courses/{{courseId}}/assignments

###############################################################################
### COMPLETIONS: Who completed an assignment
###############################################################################

### List students who completed an assignment
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/completions

### Get single assignment
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/assignments/{{assignmentId}}
